*gparted-0.3.8 (23 Jul 2008)

  23 Jul 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org> -gparted-0.3.6.ebuild,
  -gparted-0.3.7.ebuild, +gparted-0.3.8.ebuild:
  bump to 0.3.8. Various bug fixes and translation updates. Hal isn't
  necessary anymore, dropping patch.

*gparted-0.3.7-r1 (15 Jun 2008)

  15 Jun 2008; Gilles Dartiguelongue <eva@gentoo.org>
  +files/gparted-0.3.7-hal-lock.patch, +gparted-0.3.7-r1.ebuild:
  do not fail in absence of hal, bug #220459. 
  more su helper sweetness, bug #220383.

